data.description: Located only 3 blocks from Lake Houston, this home is perfect for water enthusiasts. This 3-bedroom, 2 bathroom home boasts a unique feature - a boat driveway! The primary bedroom offers a peaceful retreat with an en-suite bathroom featuring a spa-like soaking tub and a separate shower. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Lake Houston gem your own!
